rlRfPALoopbackCfg_t Struct Reference

Radar RF PA loopback configuration. More...

#include <control/mmwavelink/include/rl_sensor.h>

Data Fields

rlUInt16_t paLoopbackFreq
 value is a 100MHz divider which sets the loopback frequency
For e.g. for a 1 MHz frequency, set this to 10
For a 2 MHz frequency, set this to 50
Note: To ensure no leakage of signal power, user has to ensure that
100MHz/LOOPBACK_FREQ is an integer multiple of bin width For e.g. if user
choses 25Msps sampling rate and 2048 samples/chirp, then
LOOPBACK_FREQ of 64 (=1.5625MHz) will ensure no leakage

 
rlUInt8_t paLoopbackEn
 Enable/Disable PA loopback
1: PA loopback Enable, 0: PA loopback Disable
.
 
rlUInt8_t reserved
 Reserved for Future use.
